'''基斯甸·比歷克'''（{{lang-pl|Krystian Bielik}}，{{IPA-pl|ˈkrɨstjan ˈbjɛlik|pron}}，{{bd|1998年|1月4日}}），是一名[[波蘭|波蘭]]職業足球員，現效力於[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]和[[波蘭國家足球隊|波蘭國家足球隊]]。司職[[中堅|中堅]]、[[防守中場|防守中場]]。

2014年，比歷克於[[歷基亞足球俱樂部|歷基亞]]開始其職業生涯，於1年後轉會至[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]。2016-17賽季的下半季，他被外借至[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]。

在國家隊方面，他曾為波蘭 U19上陣。

==球會生涯==
=== 歷基亞 ===
比歷克於其家鄉球會{{link-en|科寧足球俱樂部|Górnik Konin|科寧}}的青年隊開始踢球，2012年，他被[[波兹南莱克足球俱樂部|波茲南萊克]]的球探發現，並邀請他加入球會的青年隊。效力期間，他贏得波蘭 U17聯賽的冠軍<ref>{{cite web|title=MP juniorów młodszych - 3. kolejka|url=http://www.90minut.pl/news/234/news2345100-MP-juniorow-mlodszych---3-kolejka.html|publisher=90minut.pl|accessdate=2015-01-16|language=pl|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005154916/http://www.90minut.pl/news/234/news2345100-MP-juniorow-mlodszych---3-kolejka.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。可是，在2014年7月，他以8800歐元的價錢轉會至主要競爭對手[[歷基亞足球俱樂部|歷基亞]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Krystian Bielik zawodnikiem Legii|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/krystian-bielik-zawodnikiem-legii-42342|publisher=Legia Warsaw|accessdate=2015-01-16|date=2014-07-04|language=pl|archive-date=2019-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803075748/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/krystian-bielik-zawodnikiem-legii-42342|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title= Klub z V ligi zarobi na wychowanku. Bo Bielik startował z Konina|url= http://www.poznan.sport.pl/sport-poznan/1,124479,17263313,Klub_z_V_ligi_zarobi_na_wychowanku__Bo_Bielik_startowal.html|publisher= sport.pl|accessdate= 2015-01-16|date= 2015-01-16|language= pl|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://archive.is/20150118205801/http://www.poznan.sport.pl/sport-poznan/1,124479,17263313,Klub_z_V_ligi_zarobi_na_wychowanku__Bo_Bielik_startowal.html|archivedate= 2015-01-18}}</ref>。8月24日，他在對陣[[凱爾采科羅納足球俱樂部|凱爾采科羅納]]時首次於[[波蘭足球甲級聯賽|波蘭足球甲級聯賽]]上陣<ref>{{cite web|title=Krystian Bielik zadebiutował w ekstraklasie. "W nocy budziłem się po 2-3 razy"|url=http://www.sportowefakty.pl/pilka-nozna/462853/krystian-bielik-zadebiutowal-w-ekstraklasie-w-nocy-budzilem-sie-po-2-3-razy|publisher=Sportowefakty.pl|accessdate=2015-01-16|language=pl|archive-date=2015-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121053527/http://www.sportowefakty.pl/pilka-nozna/462853/krystian-bielik-zadebiutowal-w-ekstraklasie-w-nocy-budzilem-sie-po-2-3-razy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 阿仙奴 ===
2015年1月21日，比歷克轉會至[[阿仙奴足球俱樂部|阿仙奴]]，但官方並没有透露轉會金額。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/20150121/arsenal-complete-krystian-bielik-deal|title=Arsenal complete Krystian Bielik deal|publisher=Arsenal F.C.|date=2015-01-21|accessdate=2015-01-21|language=en|archive-date=2015-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121134551/http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/20150121/arsenal-complete-krystian-bielik-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref>
2015年10月27日，比歷克於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對陣[[錫周三足球會|錫周三]]，於第60分鐘入替同是首次上陣的[[格連·卡馬拉|格連·卡馬拉]]，但阿仙奴作客以3比0落敗<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34578025|title=Sheffield Wednesday 3-0 Arsenal|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2015-10-28|accessdate=2015-10-28|language=en|archive-date=2015-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026223527/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34578025|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 伯明翰（外借） ===
2017年1月31日，比歷克被外借至[[英格蘭冠軍足球聯賽|英格蘭冠軍足球聯賽]]球隊[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]，直至賽季完結<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/38798273 |title=Birmingham sign Arsenal's Krystian Bielik and Watford's Jerome Sinclair on loan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2017-01-31 |accessdate=2017-06-05 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029210634/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/38798273 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月14日，他在對陣[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯顿]]時首次為球隊上陣，並打滿全場，但球隊以1比2落敗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-player-ratings-how-12605973 |title=Birmingham City player ratings: How Blues performed against Preston |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2017-02-14 |accessdate=2017-02-15 |language=en |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402162007/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-player-ratings-how-12605973 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10日後，球隊中堅[[保羅·羅賓遜_(1978年出生後衛)|保羅·羅賓遜]]在對陣[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]時被球證出示紅牌逐出場，比歷克後備入替，與{{link-en|瑞恩·紹頓|Ryan Shotton}}出任中堅的位置，最終伯明翰以2比1勝出<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39000455 |title=Wolverhampton Wanderers 12 Birmingham City |first=Tom |last=Garry |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2017-02-24 |accessdate=2017-06-05 |language=en |archive-date=2019-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328172842/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39000455 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後在3月中，伯明翰對陣[[紐卡素足球會|紐卡素]]的比賽時，比歷克、保羅·羅賓遜和瑞恩·紹頓組成的三中堅防線保持不失球，其中比歷克良好的表現成功令領隊[[吉安弗蘭科·佐拉|-{zh-hans:吉安弗兰科·佐拉;zh-hk:基安法蘭高·蘇拿;zh-tw:吉安弗蘭科·佐拉;}-]]繼續讓他於接下來的數星期聯賽中出任正選，球隊亦考慮於2017-18賽季繼續租借他<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/krystian-bielik-scouting-report-how-12765187 |title=Krystian Bielik scouting report: How the Arsenal loanee's Birmingham City career is going so far |first=Shane |last=Ireland |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2017-03-19 |accessdate=2017-06-05 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925010714/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/krystian-bielik-scouting-report-how-12765187 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/birmingham-city-manager-gianfranco-zola-12853821 |title=Birmingham City manager Gianfranco Zola discusses the future of Arsenal defender Krystian Bielik |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2017-04-06 |accessdate=2017-06-05 |language=en |archive-date=2019-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017225016/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/birmingham-city-manager-gianfranco-zola-12853821 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

可是，由於基安法蘭高·蘇拿因成績欠佳而辭職，接任的[[哈里·雷德克纳普|-{zh-hans:哈里·雷德克纳普;zh-hk:哈利·列納;zh-tw:哈里·雷德克納普;}-]]改變球隊的陣式至四後衛<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-comment-how-harry-13003205 |title=Birmingham City comment: How Harry Redknapp saved Blues |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2017-05-08 |accessdate=2017-06-05 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030214405/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/birmingham-city-comment-how-harry-13003205 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再加上[[迈克尔·莫里森|-{zh-hans:迈克尔·莫里森; zh-hk:米高·摩理臣; zh-tw:邁克爾·莫里森;}-]]復出，比歷克失去正選位置，只在聯賽煞科戰作客對陣[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔城]]的比賽中上陣。他協助球隊保持1比0的比數至完場，避免球隊降班至[[英格蘭甲組足球聯賽|英格蘭甲組足球聯賽]]<ref name=sb1617/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/bristol-city-vs-birmingham-city-12989133 |title=Bristol City vs Birmingham City live: Adams gives Blues early lead; Blackburn lead at Brentford |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=2017-05-07 |accessdate=2017-06-05 |language=en |archive-date=2019-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031152555/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/bristol-city-vs-birmingham-city-12989133 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 華素爾（外借） ===
比歷克因肩傷無法於2017年夏季轉會窗外借。2018年1月31日，他被外借至[[英格蘭甲組足球聯賽|英格蘭甲組足球聯賽]]球會[[沃爾索爾足球俱樂部|華素爾]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.expressandstar.com/sport/football/walsall-fc/2018/01/31/walsall-sign-krystian-bielik-on-loan-from-arsenal/ |title=Deal: Walsall sign Krystian Bielik on loan from Arsenal |first=Joseph |last=Masi |newspaper=Express & Star |location=Wolverhampton |date=2018-01-31 |accessdate=2018-02-01 |language=en |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330214007/https://www.expressandstar.com/sport/football/walsall-fc/2018/01/31/walsall-sign-krystian-bielik-on-loan-from-arsenal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 查爾頓（外借） ===
2018年8月16日，比歷克被外借至[[查爾頓競技足球俱樂部|查爾頓]]，為期1個賽季<ref>{{cite news |title=DONE DEAL: Charlton sign Krystian Bielik on loan from Arsenal |url=https://www.cafc.co.uk/news/view/5b745dedc58ac/done-deal-charlton-sign-krystian-bielik-on-loan-from-arsenal |accessdate=2018-08-16 |publisher=Charlton Athletic F.C. |date=2018-08-16 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128052842/https://www.cafc.co.uk/news/view/5b745dedc58ac/done-deal-charlton-sign-krystian-bielik-on-loan-from-arsenal |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title= Krystian Bielik: Charlton Athletic sign Arsenal midfielder on loan|url= https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/45209306|language= en|date= 2018-08-16|work= BBC|accessdate= 2018-09-02|archive-date= 2020-04-14|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200414004953/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/45209306|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

=== 德比郡 ===
2019年8月2日，别利克转会至德比郡，并与其签约5年<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rams Sign Youngster Bielik From Arsenal|url=https://www.dcfc.co.uk/news/2019/08/rams-sign-youngster-bielik-from-arsenal|accessdate=2019-09-05|work=www.dcfc.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218065428/https://www.dcfc.co.uk/news/2019/08/rams-sign-youngster-bielik-from-arsenal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

